song.name: President Block
song.songnotes: Bent: "Another cover that worked really well, the original was done by a local Trondheim band- «Epinastic Movements» on a 3 song 12" in 1993. This 12" was printed in 500 copies, of which around 250 were faulty, making it somewhat of a collectors item. The band also released a 5 song CD called «Rapid» and did approx 20 gigs before calling it a day. The reason why we recorded our version of P.B., was that both bands wanted to do a split-7" of eachothers material. They wanted to do an electric «Come on in», and - if memory serves me right - also recorded it in Brygga Studios, but split up before we got that far. Good band, though, and mr Stenøien is one hell of a song-writer, dontcha think?"
